  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-runner</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-runner</application> package provides a tool used
      to launch programs quickly by typing their names.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked; &gcc5_checked;

